@startuml cicd_diagram

title Votacao Backend - CI/CD Pipelines (GitHub Actions — push to main)

actor Desenvolvedor

rectangle "workflow-frontend.yml" as wf_front {
    rectangle "code-quality-frontend\n(ESLint + Prettier check)" as lint_f
    rectangle "test-frontend\n(Vitest + coverage)" as test_f
    rectangle "coverage-frontend\n(threshold gate + Codecov upload)" as cov_f
}

rectangle "workflow-backend-associados.yml" as wf_assoc {
    rectangle "code-quality-associados\n(Checkstyle / PMD / SpotBugs)" as quality_a
    rectangle "test-associados\n(Maven clean package + JaCoCo + Codecov)" as test_a
    rectangle "build-associados\n(Maven -DskipTests + artefato JAR)" as build_a
}

rectangle "workflow-backend-pautas.yml" as wf_pautas {
    rectangle "code-quality-pautas\n(Checkstyle / PMD / SpotBugs)" as quality_p
    rectangle "test-pautas\n(Maven clean package + JaCoCo + Codecov)" as test_p
    rectangle "build-pautas\n(Maven -DskipTests + artefato JAR)" as build_p
}

rectangle "workflow-backend-sessoes.yml" as wf_sessoes {
    rectangle "code-quality-sessoes\n(Checkstyle / PMD / SpotBugs)" as quality_s
    rectangle "test-sessoes\n(Maven clean package + JaCoCo + Codecov)" as test_s
    rectangle "build-sessoes\n(Maven -DskipTests + artefato JAR)" as build_s
}

Desenvolvedor --> wf_front : git push main
Desenvolvedor --> wf_assoc : git push main
Desenvolvedor --> wf_pautas : git push main
Desenvolvedor --> wf_sessoes : git push main

lint_f --> test_f
test_f --> cov_f

quality_a --> test_a
test_a --> build_a

quality_p --> test_p
test_p --> build_p

quality_s --> test_s
test_s --> build_s

note right of wf_front
    Perfis de threshold de cobertura:
    - baseline: limiar atual
    - nextSprint: limiar + 2 p.p. (continue-on-error)
    Upload para Codecov via OIDC
end note

note right of wf_assoc
    api-gateway e service-discovery
    possuem workflows próprios nos
    seus repositórios separados.
end note

@enduml